# rhu-dashboard

A dashboard project for the Rural Health Unit (RHU).
Includes disease surveillance and reporting features.

## Installation
1. Clone the repository: `git clone https://github.com/smagdangal2026/rhu-dashboard.git`
2. Navigate to the project folder: `cd rhu-dashboard`
3. Install dependencies: `npm install`

## Usage
Run the project locally:
```bash
npm start
